<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentc40989209abb454a815a7460b10e62d0">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Assessment and Treatment Centre, Chorley and South Ribble Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1882"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Chorley and South Ribble Hospital provides a range of district general hospital services including general medicine, surgery, orthopaedics, stroke rehabilitation and breast care.</p>
<p>Our Centre for Health Research and Innovation undertakes a wide variety of clinical studies and trials to develop new drugs and treatments.</p>
<p>We provide award winning education programmes for medical, nursing and allied health professional students in our state of the art learning facilities which are amongst the most advanced in the country.</p>
<p>Our purpose is to always provide excellent care with compassion.  We believe every single patient deserves the very highest standards of care, and to be treated with kindness and respect. </p>
<p>For more information about our hospital and services please visit our website:</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p></div>
